REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS

Title: Relates to the definition of New York state labelled beer
Summary: Relates to the definition of New York state labelled beer; requires such labelled beer to be processed in New York state.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to the definition of New York state labelled beer
